@node INTRODUCTION "Introduction"

                                  @{b}Introduction@{ub}

Pkb.mcc is a Custom Class of the @{"Magic User Interface" link MUI} © by Stefan Stuntz.
It's a subclass of Virtgroup-class.

The aim of this class is to provide a piano keyboard for generic music
applications.

@endnode
@node INSTALLING "Installation"

  @{b}@{u}Requirements@{uu} @{ub}

Kickstart V39 (OS 3.x) or above.
68020 or better.
@{"MagicUserInterface" Link MUI} V3.6 or above.


    To install Pkb simply copy the contents of the libs/ directory
to MUI:libs/mui/

    If you are a developer and you want to use the class, copy the developer
files to their respective locations. Developers must inform me if they
are using this class to ensure they get any news/updates!

@endnode
